dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:43:19.000Z","msg":"比沙路呢？"},{"pid":"9fde43d0b49ec65faea16bc1f22613cf402d4595","tid":1242490,"uid":257422,"like":24,"dislike":11,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:43:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議，認同請幫手推post：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98139e50a80856fa416b6728c037cad513db70c","tid":1242490,"uid":81037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"至少入到世界盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b017de669e8089b1dfc3ac257616c3974afe2d1","tid":1242490,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:32:16.000Z","msg":"維度，山狗，華加斯，艾蘭古斯，富恩沙列達，文拿，<br />\n巴禾（傷）"},{"pid":"c40fec71e7ec24d1bf4ced5c58a0690df7e4c7d4","tid":1242490,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87efbc5a5ad4589142f9f97b4cf8fce7c306e0a2","tid":1242490,"uid":38189,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"花迷覺得法芬勁過成隊阿根廷"},{"pid":"e2605bc7c8ad4cab33b9c063b01fb6b41980fab5","tid":1242490,"uid":37220,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:17:30.000Z","msg":"法芬我細細個就聽過呢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6476de4774c4dc642f4442d7792b85c838a3d75","tid":1242490,"uid":82938,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e2605bc7c8ad4cab33b9c063b01fb6b41980fab5","tid":1242490,"uid":37220,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:17:30.000Z","msg":"法芬我細細個就聽過呢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:19:26.000Z","msg":"世界盃好慘 第1場踢足 第2場半場入黎<br />\n第3場腦震盪missed"},{"pid":"fd0c40faea1d79d1cf9845de3c75ade30edaff92","tid":1242490,"uid":37220,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"f6476de4774c4dc642f4442d7792b85c838a3d75","tid":124